Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,农家的媳妇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.41,0:00:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我的老家在乡下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,还是非常偏僻的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道未婚妻受不受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.89,0:00:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,就说要试试她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.69,0:00:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要是可以撑过去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就可以结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之前都不可以做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我想问路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.51,0:00:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.45,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,已经迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.45,0:01:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这边全都
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.52,0:01:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是他的地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.06,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有厕所啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,走要30分钟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这边可以上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,别偷看啊
