Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你的鞋会走烂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是正男的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这就我家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你是儿子?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟你爸要结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.62,0:07:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.15,0:07:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是妓女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快舔\N误会啊
