Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.32,0:09:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,见过我儿子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.39,0:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你儿子这麽大了
