Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.61,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要一起加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我带你看
